WEBVTT

00:06:28.456 --> 00:06:30.918
whereas now, it supports tens of millions.

00:06:30.942 --> 00:06:34.037
CA: And so, the difference
between your survival and otherwise

00:06:34.061 --> 00:06:38.760
is human knowledge turned into technology,

00:06:38.784 --> 00:06:43.925
which has built the house, the central
heating, the clothes and so forth,

00:06:43.949 --> 00:06:45.815
that keep you alive.

00:06:45.839 --> 00:06:47.823
DD: Yes, fundamentally, it's knowledge.

00:06:47.847 --> 00:06:50.083
CA: And when you talk about,
you know, like,

00:06:50.107 --> 00:06:53.589
that humans can have
indefinite impact on the universe

00:06:53.613 --> 00:06:56.910
through Star Trek-like expansion out,

00:06:56.934 --> 00:06:59.809
at first glance, a lot of people
listening to that will say,

00:06:59.833 --> 00:07:01.992
well, already that's sounding
a little silly,